1. Distribution & Credits

The source audio recordings utilized in this project are derived from the University of Iowa Musical Instrument Samples project.
Credit for the source recordings belongs exclusively to the University of Iowa.
Source: https://theremin.music.uiowa.edu/MIS-Pitches-2012/MISDoubleBass2012.html

2. Technical Engineering & Open Source Logic

My role in this project was the technical translation, spectral analysis, G-Point (transient) calibration, and optimization for the DecentSampler engine.
The software code, scripts, and XML structural logic created by the author (LAG) are released under the MIT License.

